plptool.mips

Class SimCore.ex

  • java.lang.Object
    • plptool.mips.SimCore.ex
  • Enclosing class:
    SimCore

    public class SimCore.ex
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the execute (EX) stage of the PLP CPU pipeline. The memory and ALU modules are attached to this class.
